long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Stick Merge Master Class is an engaging blend of casual action 🎮 and strategic merging gameplay, designed by the creative minds at TinyDobbins.

In this game, your mission is to amalgamate diverse weapon types 🔫 to forge mightier firearms, which you'll then employ against animated stick figures in a dynamic shooting range environment.

Gear up your arsenal, elevate your handgun's capabilities, discover every power-up 🚀 at your disposal, and rise to become the preeminent marksman in the metropolis.

The question at the heart of Stick Merge Master Class is just how formidable you can become. 🌟 Join us in this adventure to uncover your true potential!
